{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "铁大爷要从二十九名丝士中选二十七人，多余的必须死。老者王中平和少年阿干拒绝就死。阿干暴起扑杀高师爷，反被丝网困住、银刺穿喉而死，割头小鬼随即割走他的头颅。柳明秋向慕容透露楚留香已死于林还玉之手，慕容震惊。王中平被一白袍女子拥抱后中毒身亡，死前留下预言：铁大爷此战必败，因为那个瞎子的身份他们永远猜不到。铁大爷与丝路对此不以为意。决战定在中秋月圆夜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有死人才能绝对保守秘密。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是句非常正确而且非常聪明的话，我却不是第一个说这句话的人，我还没有这么聪明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是现在这句话已经是大家都明白的至理名言了，你们一定也明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要的是二十七个人，现在却有二十九，",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们说，现在我该怎么办?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "丝士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我们常常都挤在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "丝士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且我们喜欢两个人挤在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "丝路其实并不是一条路，他那班兄弟虽然认为没有他就无路可走，有了他，其实也一样无路可走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "如果说，他真的是一条路，那么这条路一定是用别人的尸体铺出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我敢说铁老大带去的那五十骑中，至少已经死了十九个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "五十，减十九，还剩三十一。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "二十七个藏身处，二十七个人，现在为什么还有三十一个活着?难道铁老大和那条路都不明白只有死人才能守口?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "丝士中有好几对都亲密如兄弟手足夫妻，尤其是其中的林家兄弟和青山兄弟，更是分不开的，所以虽然只有二十七个藏身处，却可能有二十九个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "三十一，减二十九，好像还有两个。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对不对?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "还有两个人呢?为什么还能够活到现在?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "其实我不说你应该知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为这两个人都是你已经老早听说过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "铁乌龟的五大爱将，枯、老、大、女、少，都不可能在这种时候出现的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "其中最多只有两个会出现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一老一少，如果我说得不对，我罚酒，罚三杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "王老身经百战，已经从无数次杀人的经验中，体会出一种最有效的刺击术，他自己命名为一百刺，九十九中。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他当然不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他已经六十九，连死都不怕了，还怕什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "如果我已经六十九，我只怕一件事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "到那时候，我只怕还没有死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你十六七岁的时候呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那时候我怕死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那时候我只要一看到死人，我就会哭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为你是个养尊处优的贵公子，你从小的日子就是过得很快乐的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我想你在十二三岁的时候，就已经把你们家的丫头都欺负死了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "可是有很多人都不是这样子的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他们都跟你不同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "有什么不同?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你没有想到死，可是你怕死，如果你死了，你的好爸爸、好妈妈、好姐姐、好妹妹，好衣裳、好吃的、好玩的，一下子全部没有了，所以你想不怕死都不行，因为你有太多只有你活着才能享受的东西。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是另外一些人呢?他们为什么也不怕死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不怕死，只因为他们什么都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "那个叫阿干的小男孩，就是这样子的，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他没有父母，没有朋友，没有爱，他不怕死，他只怕一个人孤孤单单活在这个没希没望的世界里，有人逼他，他只有干。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "依我看来他当然有几分可以去干一番出生入死的本事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "如果这小子能活到二十岁，我敢说他比谁都行，也许比当年楚留香在二十岁的时候都行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你把他跟楚留香比?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你比的是不是那个楚留香?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "天下有几个楚留香?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "那么我说的就是这一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这个世界上，天才本来就不多，如果连二十岁都活不到，那就太可惜了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你是在说阿干?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "难道你已算准他活不到二十岁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "text": "王老先生，看起来你大概已经不行了，连割头小鬼都不要你的头了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "text": "如果他还要你的头，他一定会等你先死了之后才来割头。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "text": "你走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "text": "如果连小鬼都不要你的头了，我这个老鬼怎么还会要你的命?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "是的，看起来我好像真的已经老了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "老人的头就好像丑妇的身体一样，通常都没有什么人想要的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "text": "看起来，世上好像的确有很多事都是这样子的。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "一点都不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对大多数人来说，丝路的意思，就是死路，就算他偶然给别人一条活路，那条路也细如游丝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "所以阿干现在应该已经是个死人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一定?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "铁大爷要他死，那个只穿绿丝袍的老怪物也要他死，我们好像也不想他再活下去，这个世界上，还有谁能救他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "好像还有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "这个世界上无论发生了多么不可思议不能解决的事，好像总有一种人可以解决的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这种人是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "这种人好像就是你刚刚提起的那个楚留香。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你在干什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "看起来，你好像在伤心。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "好像是有一点。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你为什么要伤心?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为我知道连楚留香也救不了阿干了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为楚留香在三个月之前，就已经是个死人。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "楚留香真的已经死了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你有把握?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我有!",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "本来我也不信他会死的，深沉阴险如无花和尚和南宫灵，绝艳惊才如水母和石观音，他们都不能要他死，还有谁能?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "可是他的确死了，是死在一个女人手里的，一个美似天仙，其实却如同魔鬼一样的女人。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "她的名字叫林还玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "林还玉?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "还君明珠双泪垂，还君宝玉君已死。君死妾丧情亦绝，天上地下永不聚。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "这一定也是极尽悱恻缠绵让人爱得你死我活的故事，幸好我现在根本不想听。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "现在我他妈的根本没心情来听这种见了活鬼的狗屁故事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有用的，绝对没有用的。",
      "tone": "怨毒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随便你们怎么设计，这一次你们还是必败无疑。",
      "tone": "怨毒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那个瞎子，你们如果知道他是谁，说不定现在就会一头撞死。",
      "tone": "怨毒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王中平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你们永远也不会知道他是谁的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好香，真的香。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪有学问的人都说，只有兰花的香气，才是王者之香。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "难道楚香帅那种名闻天下的郁金花香气，也比不上?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "当然比不上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "因为那种香气现在已经没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "是不是因为楚留香这个人现在也已经没有了?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    }
